text: There are communes that have the name Meslay in France: *Meslay, Calvados, in the Calvados département *Meslay, Loir-et-Cher, in the Loir-et-Cher département *Meslay-du-Maine, in the Mayenne département *Meslay-le-Grenet, in the Eure-et-Loir département *Meslay-le-Vidame, in the Eure-et-Loir département
title: Meslay
